Hon. Ladi Adebutu faction of the Peopleâ€™s Democratic Party ( PDP ) on Thursday afternoon adopted Hon. Abdulkabir Adekunle Akinlade of the Allied Peoples Movement (APM) as its governorship candidate for the Saturday gubernatorial election in Ogun state. The deal was sealed at the Park Inn, Abeokuta, the state capital, with the factional Chairman of PDP in the State, Hon. Sikirullai Ogundele. Ogundele told reporters that the faction found Akinlade more credible and competent to govern the state than other contestants.